# Flutter/Dart/Pub related
# Libraries should not include pubspec.lock, per https://dart.dev/guides/libraries/private-files#pubspeclock.
/pubspec.lock
**/doc/api/
.dart_tool/
.flutter-plugins-dependencies
/build/
/coverage/

# /docs/ contains a mix of tracked design specs and untracked working notes.
# Track: docs/superpowers/, docs/ai/ (committed design specs and AI-generated docs)
# Ignore: docs/plans/ (working drafts, not source-of-truth)
/docs/plans/

.reference/

.worktrees/
